data.title: Shouwang Zhengfeng Shen Jiang Zhi Nu
Fengyu Lang Qiao
data.synopsis: In the troubled times at the end of the Tang Dynasty, the cannibalism spreads. The knight-errant who used to wield his sword has become an old man suffering from old illnesses, living cautiously in order to feed his hunger. Until he meets a little girl, and his dormant fighting spirit and humanity are re-awakened.
